 ## Core Technology
 
 High-pressure drop-stitch inflatable construction using coated textile materials.
 
-When pressurized, thousands of internal threads maintain structure rigidity.
+When pressurized to 10 to 15 PSI, thousands of internal threads maintain structural rigidity. The platform supports up to 650 lbs under professional use conditions.
 
-Applications include:
+This same technology class is already used in stand-up paddleboards, inflatable rescue platforms, and high-performance inflatable boats. Sidekick Air is the first professional application in the therapy platform market.
 
-- therapy tables
-- emergency stretchers
-- medical gurneys
-- sports recovery platforms
-- portable rehabilitation systems
