 ## Product Architecture
 
-Components include:
+The system has four components:
 
-- inflatable drop-stitch tabletop
-- collapsible multi-leg support stand
-- modular accessory system
-- travel transport system
+1. Inflatable drop-stitch tabletop (72" × 30" × 4")
+2. Collapsible multi-leg support stand
+3. Modular accessory system (face cradle, expanders, anchors)
+4. Rolling travel case with pump storage
 
